【Sturdy Stable & Durable & Safe】: This corner bookcase is made of high-grade MDF board and durable metal tube frame to ensure good quality, and each shelf can hold up to 22 lbs. The four-leg stand design and the included extra anti-tip kit secure the shelf to the wall, ensuring stability and safety for the corner book shelf.

【Urban Industrial and Fashionable Design】: The classic combination of rustic brown and black of the 5-tier corner standing shelf combines the charm of classical and modern furniture styles, showing a sense of luxury in a low-key manner. Unique wood grain finishes collide with metallic elements for an industrial feel, creating a calm and fresh vibe in your room that easily blends into any decor. The perfect combination of decorative and functional uses.

【Easy to Assemble】: This corner shelf organizer has a simple structure, and the package contains detailed instructions. Combined with the specific installation method of the corner shelves standing introduced in the video, the whole installation process is extremely simple, and the corner cabinet shelf can be assembled in about 5-10 minutes. Perfectly situated in my busiest room, it's proven invaluable for storing my reading materials and showcasing my favorite indoor plants. The built-in two USB and standard charging ports are a brilliant addition; my phone and tablet are always within reach and charged. Assembly was a breeze, and its blend of utility with style has made this stand a delightful addition. It's now an essential part of my room, and I can't recommend it enough
